#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:360
msgid "Gu! You are wounded! What is happening?!"
msgstr "Gu ! Tu es blessé ! Qu'est-ce qui se passe ?!"

#. [message], speaker=Gu
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:365
msgid "(dying) Orcs are attacking. I was not able to stop them."
msgstr "<i>mourant</i> Les orcs attaquent. Je n'ai pas réussi à les arrêter."

#. [message], speaker=Gu
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:370
msgid "We have been friends for a long time… but you can’t do anything for poor Gu anymore."
msgstr "Nous sommes amis depuis longtemps… mais tu ne peux plus rien pour le pauvre Gu."

#. [message], speaker=Gu
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:375
msgid "Go to Zei. Find Csia."
msgstr "Va à Zei. Trouve Csia."

#. [message], speaker=Gu
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:380
msgid "If the orcs also betrayed us there, the king will need you."
msgstr "Si les orcs nous ont aussi trahi là-bas, le roi aura besoin de toi."

#. [message], speaker=Gu
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:385
msgid "Go, now! *dies*"
msgstr "Va, maintenant! <i>meurt</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:396
msgid "Gu! No!"
msgstr "Gu ! Non!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:401
msgid "Friends! To arms! We must free our land from the orcs!"
msgstr "Amis ! Aux armes! On doit libérer nos terres des orcs !"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:406
msgid "A few things will be a bit unusual in this campaign. Io can pick up and equip items. You won't lose any gold if you have a negative income. However, you won't get much gold at the beginning of scenarios beside what you had at the end of the previous one. If you get stuck at the beginning of a scenario, then it might be that you ended the previous one with too little gold. You will be able to sell the objects you have gathered in shops in exchange for gold, so don't forget to collect as many objects as you can."
msgstr "Quelques choses seront inhabituelles dans cette camapgne. Io peut ramasser et équiper des objets. Vous ne perdrez pas d'or si vous avez un revenu négatif. Cependant, vous n'obtiendrez pas beaucoup d'or au début des scénarios à part celui que vous aviez à la fin du précédent. Si vous vous retrouvez bloqués au début d'un scénario, cela peut vouloir dire que vous avez terminé le précédent avec trop peu d'or. Vous pourrez vendre les objets que vous aurez collectés dans des boutiques pour de l'or, alors n'oubliez pas de collecter autant d'objets que possible."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:417
msgid ""
"It is not with my fists that I will fight against orcs. I need a weapon. \n"
"Let's grab this knife."
msgstr ""
"Ce n'est pas avec mes poings que je vais combattre les orcs. J'ai besoin d'une arme\n"
"Prenons ce couteau."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:432
msgid "This is better. Now I can strike faster and harder."
msgstr "C'est mieux. Maintenant je peux frapper plus vite et plus fort."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:436
msgid ""
"If I find any, I could also use other weapons. \n"
"Clubs are like knifes, but more smashy and less stabby. Meanwhile, spears are more powerful, but a bit slow."
msgstr ""
"Si j'en trouve, je pourrais également utiliser d'autres armes.\n"
"Les gourdins sont comme les couteaux, mais plus frappant et moins coupant. Les lances elles sont plus puissantes, mais un peu lentes."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:450
msgid ""
"To bad I am such a bad leader.\n"
"I am afraid I won't be able to manage more than 10 allies at once."
msgstr ""
"Dommage que je soit un si mauvais chef.\n"
"J'ai bien peur de ne pouvoir gérer plus de 10 alliés d'un coup."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:465
msgid "Poor Owepaup. He burnt with his house."
msgstr "Pauvre Owepaup. Il a brûlé avec sa maison."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:469
msgid "Wait! I found something!"
msgstr "Attends! J'ai trouvé quelque chose!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:473
msgid "It looks like a half-burnt book. Might be useful."
msgstr "On dirait un livre à moitié brûlé. Ça pourrait servir"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:495
msgid "We have no time to kill all the orcs. We must hurry to Zei."
msgstr "On n'a pas le temps de tuer tous les orcs. On doit se dépêcher d'aller à Zei."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:506
msgid "Wait for us! We will try to kill some more orcs before leaving."
msgstr "Attends nous! On va essayer de tuer quelques orcs de plus avant de partir."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:531
msgid "The orcs are all dead!"
msgstr "Les orcs sont tous morts!"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:535
msgid "It looks like this one was going to leave with valuables stolen to our friends. At least we were able to recover that."
msgstr "On dirait que celui-ci allait partir avec des choses de valeurs volées à nos amis. Au moins, on aura réussi à récupérer ça."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:539
msgid " I hope nothing happened in Zei. Let's go find out."
msgstr "J'espère que rien ne s'est produit à Zei. Allons voir."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\01_Fate_of_a_Farmer.cfg:555
msgid "We can't even kill a few orcs on our land. How could we imagine reaching Zei?"
msgstr "On n'est même pas capable de tuer quelques orcs sur nos terres. Comment a-t-on pu imaginer atteindre Zei?"

#. [scenario], id=02_Helping_neighbors
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:5
msgid "Helping neighbors"
msgstr "Au secours des Voisins"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:40
msgid "Move Io to the signpost at the south-west end of the map."
msgstr "Déplacer Io jusqu'au panneau au bord sud-ouest de la carte."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:45
msgid "Defeat all enemy leaders"
msgstr "Vaincre tous les chefs ennemis"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:213
msgid "There might be a lot of orcs here too. We need to be careful."
msgstr "Il y a probablement beaucoup d'orcs ici aussi. On va devoir être prudent."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:218
msgid "The bridge to Zei is south of here. Let's go."
msgstr "Le pont pour Zei est au sud d'ici. Allons-y."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:234
msgid "It smells like death in here."
msgstr "Ça sent la mort la dedans."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:253
msgid "So that's why."
msgstr "Ah, voilà pourquoi."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:270
msgid "I wonder if Hexe is still alive. Let's look inside."
msgstr "Je me demande si Hexe is toujours en vie. Voyons voir."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:275
msgid "Alas, he was killed by an orc."
msgstr "Malheureusement, il a été tué par un orc."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:289
msgid "Anyway, I found a book upstairs. Maybe it contains information."
msgstr "Par contre, j'ai trouvé un livre à l'étage. Peut-être qu'il contient des informations."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:311
msgid "It looks like Izu is still alive."
msgstr "On dirait qu'Izu est toujours en vie."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:317
msgid "Hello $unit.name. I'm glad you're still alive too. I've had a rough day."
msgstr "Salut $unit.name. Je suis content de voir que tu es toujours en vie toi aussi. J'ai eu une dure journée."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:323
msgid "When I realized the orcs were attacking us, I tried to take refuge in my cave but there was a little welcoming committee in there."
msgstr "Quand j'ai réalisé que les orcs nous attaquaient, j'ai essayé de me réfugier dans ma grotte, mais il y avait un petit comité d'accueil là-bas."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:329
msgid "If you need some food for your trip to Zei and don't mind getting rid of the few orcs remaining, you can take everything you'll find in my cave."
msgstr "Si tu as besoin de nourriture pour ton voyage vers Zei et que tu ne crains pas de t'occuper des  quelques orcs qui restent, tu peut prendre tout ce que tu trouveras dans ma grotte."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:344
msgid "Thank you for getting rid of the orcs. If they chase farmers down to their homes, you might have some trouble getting to Zei, so don't waste more time here."
msgstr "Merci de m'avoir débarrassé des orcs. S'il chassent les fermiers jusqu’à leurs maisons, vous aurez probablement du mal à atteindre Zei, alors ne perdez pas votre temps ici."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:350
msgid "Here is a little present for you."
msgstr "Voilà un petit cadeau pour toi."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:357
msgid "Take care of yourself and don't worry about me. I have enough food in my cave to hold."
msgstr "Prend soin de toi et ne t'inquiète pas pour moi. J'ai assez de nourriture dans ma grotte pour tenir."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:419
msgid "There is an odd-looking brick on that wall. Should I push it?"
msgstr "Il y a une drôle de brique sur le mur. Je la pousse"

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:421
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:497
msgid "Yes, let's try."
msgstr "Oui, essaye."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:465
msgid "That's clever."
msgstr "C'est malin."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:471
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:521
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:918
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:708
msgid "No, better not."
msgstr "Non, il ne vaut mieux pas."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:495
msgid "This wall looks fragile. I wonder what's behind. Shall I demolish it?"
msgstr "Ce mur a l'air fragile. Je me demande ce qu'il y a derrière. Je le démolis?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:515
msgid "Looks like there was a hidden room."
msgstr "On dirait une pièce secrète."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:547
msgid "We must hurry. The bridge on the river is nearby. We have to get there before something happens to it."
msgstr "On doit se dépêcher. Le pont sur la rivière est proche. On doit l'atteindre avant qu'il ne lui arrive quelque chose."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:558
msgid "Wait for us! There are still people to help here."
msgstr "Attends-nous! Il y a encore des gens à aider ici. "

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:616
msgid "The area is cleared."
msgstr "La zone est nettoyée."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:620
msgid "I found the treasure of the orcish leader."
msgstr "J'ai trouvé le trésor du chef orc."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:624
msgid "This might be useful. Let's move on and cross the bridge to Zei."
msgstr "Ça pourra être utile. On bouge et on traverse le pont pour Zei."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\02_Helping_neighbors.cfg:638
msgid "The orcs are too strong for us. We won't be able to reach Zei..."
msgstr "Les orcs sont trop forts pour nous. On n'arrivera jamais à Zei..."

#. [scenario], id=03_Bridge_to_Zei
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:4
msgid "Bridge to Zei"
msgstr "Le Pont pour Zei"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:43
msgid "Cross the bridge to Zei"
msgstr "Traverser le pont pour Zei"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:53
msgid "Find another way to Zei"
msgstr "Trouver un autre chemin pour Zei"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:63
msgid "Find the entrance to the Crypt of the Sacred Blood"
msgstr "Trouver l'entrée de la Crypte du Sang Sacré"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:74
msgid "Kill all orcs"
msgstr "Tuer tous les orcs"

#. [side]
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:322
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:400
msgid "Caged"
msgstr "Prisonniers"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:366
msgid "Finally. The bridge to Zei should be not far south."
msgstr "Enfin. Le pont pour Zei ne devrait pas être loin au sud."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:370
msgid "Let's hurry to Zei before something happens."
msgstr "Dépêchons nous d'aller à Zei avant que quelque chose n'arrive."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:374
msgid "If possible, it would be nice to kill any orcs we encounter. Our friends have suffered enough already."
msgstr "Si possible, ce serait bien de tuer tous les orcs qu'on rencontrera. Nos amis ont déjà assez souffert comme ça."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:388
msgid "Excuse me, do you happen to know what happened to the bridge?"
msgstr "Excusez-moi, vous savez ce qui est arrivé au pont ?"

#. [message], speaker=Ek
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:392
msgid "Damn orcs happened."
msgstr "Des maudits orcs, voilà ce qui est arrivé."

#. [message], speaker=Ek
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:396
msgid "I know one is as bad as another but that’s the last straw."
msgstr "Je savais qu'il n'y en avait pas un pour rattraper l'autre mais là c'est le pompon."

#. [message], speaker=Ek
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:400
msgid "They burnt the damn bridge down, then tried to cross it with their wagons while it was still on fire!"
msgstr "Ils ont brûlé le pont, et ensuite ils ont essayé de le traverser avec leur chariot pendant qu'il était toujours en feu."

#. [message], speaker=Ek
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:404
msgid "They lost half-a-dozen orcs and sabotaged their own flight plan by destroying the bridge."
msgstr "Ils ont perdu une demi-douzaine d'orcs et saboté leur propre plan de fuite en détruisant le pont."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:408
msgid "Do you know if there is another way to reach Zei?"
msgstr "Vous savez s'il y a un autre moyen de rejoindre Zei ?"

#. [message], speaker=Ek
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:412
msgid "Now, the only way to reach Zei is to pass through the old crypts by taking that road there. "
msgstr "Maintenant, la seule façon de rejoindre Zei est de passer par les vieilles cryptes en suivant cette route là."

#. [message], speaker=Ek
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:416
msgid "But don’t count on me coming with you. The way is probably full of orcs."
msgstr "Mais ne comptez pas sur moi pour venir avec vous. Le chemin est probablement infesté d'orcs."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:440
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:547
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:613
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:661
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:709
msgid "There is a bat in this cage. Should I open it?"
msgstr "Il y a une chauve-souris dans cette cage. Je l'ouvre ?"

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:442
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:549
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:615
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:663
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:711
msgid "Yes, free it."
msgstr "Oui, libère là."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:460
msgid "It is free, but I don't think it was a safe idea."
msgstr "Elle est libre, mais je ne suis pas sur que c'était une bonne idée."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:465
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:572
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:638
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:686
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:734
msgid "No, it's not a good idea. It could attack you."
msgstr "Non, ce n'est pas une bonne idée, elle pourrait t'attaquer."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:488
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:620
msgid "The staff of the statue looks like a lever. Should I try pulling it?"
msgstr "Le bâton de la statue ressemble à un levier. J'essaye de le tirer ?"

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:490
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:622
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:510
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:553
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:632
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:769
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:505
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:692
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:823
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1291
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:602
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:737
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:780
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:840
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:913
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\13_Miners_life.cfg:1197
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\13_Miners_life.cfg:1264
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\13_Miners_life.cfg:1308
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1337
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1364
#: .\scenarios\chapter3\17_Udxatfe.cfg:2877
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:455
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:480
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:686
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:703
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:793
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:818
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1028
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1045
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1135
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1160
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1205
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1272
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\26b_Troll_Fort.cfg:1339
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1604
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1626
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1921
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:933
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:955
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:997
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\34_Hive.cfg:1022
msgid "Yes, do it."
msgstr "Oui, vas-y."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:536
msgid "It looks like it opened the entrance of a secret tunnel."
msgstr "On dirait que ça a ouvert l'entrée d'un tunnel caché."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:541
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:638
msgid "No, it might be a trap."
msgstr "Non, ça pourrait être un piège."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:559
msgid ""
"North : Arable Highlands\n"
"West : Crypt of the Sacred Blood\n"
"South : Zei"
msgstr ""
"Nord : Hautes Terres Arables\n"
"Ouest : Crypte du Sang Sacré\n"
"Sud : Zei"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:579
msgid "South : Crypt of the Sacred Blood"
msgstr "Sud : Crypte du Sang Sacré"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:597
msgid "West : Crypt of the Sacred Blood"
msgstr "Ouest : Crypte du Sang Sacré"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:655
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:686
msgid "I found the entrance of the crypt."
msgstr "J'ai trouvé l'entrée de la crypte."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:659
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:690
msgid "I'm a bit worried of what we might find inside, but we have no other choice if we want to reach Zei. Let's enter the crypt but be careful everyone."
msgstr "J'ai un peu peur de ce qu'on va y trouver, mais on n'a pas le choix si on veut atteindre Zei. Entrons dans la crypte mais faites bien attention."

#. [message]
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:681
msgid "I don't see any more orc around here. We can continue our journey knowing that our friends will have a least a break."
msgstr "Je ne vois pas d'autres orcs aux alentours. On peut continuer notre voyage en sachant que nos amis auront au moins un peu de répit."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:717
msgid "Suddenly..."
msgstr "Soudain..."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:724
msgid "What is that?! A walking skeleton! What is happening here?!"
msgstr "Qu'est-ce que c'est ?! Un squelette qui marche ! Qu'est-ce qui se passe ici ?!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:755
msgid "Alas..."
msgstr "Hélas..."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:759
msgid "The bridge! It is destroyed! What happened there?! How will we be able to rally Zei now?"
msgstr "Le pont ! Il est détruit ! Qu'est-ce qui s'est passé ici ?! Comment allons nous rallier Zei maintenant ?"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:772
msgid "It will be too dangerous entering the crypt if someone is animating the dead. We'd better find a way to repair the bridge"
msgstr "Ce serait trop dangereux d'entrer dans la crypte si quelqu'un anime les morts. On ferait mieux de trouver un moyen de réparer le pont."

#. [scenario], id=04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:4
msgid "Crypt of the Sacred Blood"
msgstr "La Crypte du Sang Sacré"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:35
msgid "Reach the exit of the crypt"
msgstr "Atteindre la sortie de la crypte"

#. [side], type=Deathblade
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:85
msgid "Skeletons"
msgstr "Squelettes"

#. [side], type=Gargoyle
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:154
msgid "Gargoyles"
msgstr "Gargouilles"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:479
msgid "This skeleton we've seen up there is worrying."
msgstr "Ce squelette qu'on a vu là-haut est préoccupant."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:483
msgid "I hope no one has had the idea to animate the dead that can be found in this crypt."
msgstr "J'espère que personne n'aura eu l'idée d'animer les morts qui se trouvent dans cette crypte."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:487
msgid "Anyway, we have no choice. We must cross this crypt to reach Zei. "
msgstr "De toute façon, on n'a pas le choix. On doit traverser la crypte pour atteindre Zei."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:508
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:630
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:811
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:690
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:821
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1015
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:911
msgid "There is a large wooden door. Should I try to open it?"
msgstr "Il y a une grande porte en bois. Je l'ouvre?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:528
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:651
msgid "Part of the wall fell when I opened the door."
msgstr "Une partie du mur est tombée quand j'ai ouvert la porte."

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:533
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:710
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:798
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1036
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1310
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\09_Spider_Maze.cfg:620
msgid "Wait a bit. We'll have to open it but don't do it right now."
msgstr "Attends un peu. Nous devrons l'ouvrir mais ne le fait pas tout de suite."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:551
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\10_Great_Hall.cfg:838
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\33_Goblins_Lair.cfg:1919
msgid "There is a lever on the floor. Should I pull it?"
msgstr "Il y a un levier au sol. Je le tire?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:581
msgid "It has opened a portion of the wall."
msgstr "Ça a ouvert une portion du mur."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter1\04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:602
msgid "The portion of wall is closed back."
msgstr "La portion de mur s'est refermée."

